Module org.firebirdsql.jaybird

Package org.firebirdsql.gds.ng.wire

@InternalApi package org.firebirdsql.gds.ng.wire
Pure-java implementation of the org.firebirdsql.gds.ng API for the Firebird wire protocol.

Concrete implementations of the wire protocol are defined in packages org.firebirdsql.gds.ng.wire.version10, etc.

Since:
3.0
